==坦桑尼亞議會選舉==
坦桑尼亞議會其中264個席位由單議席選區直接選舉產生，以領先者當選，113個預留予女性的席位由政黨名單比例代表制產生，10個席位由總統委任，5席由[[桑给巴尔众议院|桑给巴尔众议院]]間接選舉產生，1席為[[當然議員|當然議員]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://freedomhouse.org/country/tanzania/freedom-world/2020 |title=Tanzania | Freedom House |accessdate=2020-10-28 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110170352/https://freedomhouse.org/country/tanzania/freedom-world/2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/tanzanian-voters-weigh-second-term-magufuli |title=Tanzanian Voters Weigh Second Term for Magufuli |publisher=VOA |date=2020-10-23 |accessdate=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130213328/https://www.voanews.com/africa/tanzanian-voters-weigh-second-term-magufuli |dead-url=no }}</ref>

截至2020年10月30日，革命黨在264個地區直選席位中已贏得至少253席。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/tanzanias-populist-leader-declared-winner-flawed-vote |title=Tanzania's Populist Leader Declared Winner of Flawed Vote |website=VOA |date=2020-10-30 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129202713/https://www.voanews.com/africa/tanzanias-populist-leader-declared-winner-flawed-vote |dead-url=no }}</ref>

